Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.230 --> 00:00:05.640
Prof: Before we begin,
I have to make a true

00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:09.000
confession to you,
my class, because you're my

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.372
