00:00:45.666 --> 00:00:48.206
UVA grad [laughter]
who always forgets Thomas

00:00:48.206 --> 00:00:49.650
Jefferson's birthday.
 

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.465
It must be a Hamiltonian mental
block [laughter]

00:00:52.465 --> 00:00:56.360
that I--it is not possible for
